How to build:
  Standard ./configure; make; make install

Dependencies:
  BLAS
  FFTW >= 3
  GSL >= 1.9
  LAPACK
  libxc >= 2.0
  perl
  bpdn (internal)
  ISF (internal)
  Qshep (internal)
  Spglib (internal)
  yaml (internal)
  arpack (optional)
  BerkeleyGW (optional)
  clBLAS (optional)
  clFFT (optional)
  ETSF_IO (optional)
  feast (optional)
  FortranCL (internal/optional)
  GD (optional)
  libISF (internal/optional)
  Metis (internal/optional)
  MPI (optional)
  NetCDF (optional)
  Newuoa (internal/optional)
  NFFT (optional)
  OpenCL (optional)
  PAPI (optional
  PFFT-Chemnitz (optional)
  PNFFT (optional)
  pspio (optional)
  ScaLAPACK/BLACS (optional)
  Parmetis (optional)
  Sparskit (optional)
  
